      {
        "ver": "v0.5.0",
        "hash": "v050-1",
        "product": "Go Agent",
        "type": "New",
        "desc": "<p><code class=\"New\" type=\"1\">New</code> Go 1.18 버전 요구</p>",
        "details": "<p>go-api 모듈의 최소 Go 버전이 1.17에서 <strong>1.18로 상향</strong>되었습니다. Go 1.18의 Generics 기능을 활용한 Wrap 함수 구현을 위해 필요합니다.</p>\n\n<div class=\"theme-admonition theme-admonition-caution alert alert--warning admonition_node\"><div class=\"admonitionHeading\"><span class=\"admonitionIcon\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.893 1.5c-.183-.31-.52-.5-.887-.5s-.703.19-.886.5L.138 13.499a.98.98 0 0 0 0 1.001c.193.31.53.501.886.501h13.964c.367 0 .704-.19.877-.5a1.03 1.03 0 0 0 .01-1.002L8.893 1.5zm.133 11.497H6.987v-2.003h2.039v2.003zm0-3.004H6.987V5.987h2.039v4.006z\"></path></svg></span>주의</div><div class=\"admonitionContent\"><p>Go 1.17 이하 버전에서는 go-api v0.5.0을 사용할 수 없습니다.</p></div></div>"
      },
      {
        "ver": "v0.5.0",
        "hash": "v050-2",
        "product": "Go Agent",
        "type": "New",
        "desc": "<p><code class=\"New\" type=\"1\">New</code> Active Stack 기능</p>",
        "details": "<p>실행 중인 트랜잭션의 goroutine 스택을 실시간으로 수집하여 병목 구간을 분석할 수 있습니다.</p>\n\n<div class=\"language-ini codeBlockContainer theme-code-block\" style=\"--prism-background-color:#292d3e;--prism-color:#f8f8f2\"><div class=\"codeBlockContent\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" class=\"prism-code language-ini codeBlock thin-scrollbar\" style=\"color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#292d3e\"><code class=\"codeBlockLines\"><span class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token key attr-name\" style=\"color:rgb(255,203,107)\">active_stack_enabled</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\">true   </span><span class=\"token comment\" style=\"color:rgb(105,112,152);font-style:italic\"># 기본값: true</span></span><br /><span class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token key attr-name\" style=\"color:rgb(255,203,107)\">active_stack_second</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\">10      </span><span class=\"token comment\" style=\"color:rgb(105,112,152);font-style:italic\"># 수집 간격 (초)</span></span><br /><span class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token key attr-name\" style=\"color:rgb(255,203,107)\">active_stack_count</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\">100      </span><span class=\"token comment\" style=\"color:rgb(105,112,152);font-style:italic\"># 최대 수집 개수</span></span></code></pre></div></div>"
      },
      {
        "ver": "v0.5.0",
        "hash": "v050-3",
        "product": "Go Agent",
        "type": "New",
        "desc": "<p><code class=\"New\" type=\"1\">New</code> 트랜잭션 연계 로그 수집 (TraceLogWriter)</p>",
        "details": "<p>로그 출력 시 현재 goroutine의 트랜잭션 정보를 자동으로 연계합니다.</p>\n\n<div class=\"language-go codeBlockContainer theme-code-block\" style=\"--prism-background-color:#292d3e;--prism-color:#f8f8f2\"><div class=\"codeBlockContent\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" class=\"prism-code language-go codeBlock thin-scrollbar\" style=\"color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#292d3e\"><code class=\"codeBlockLines\"><span class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"> </span><span class=\"token string\" style=\"color:rgb(195,232,141)\">\"github.com/whatap/go-api/logsink\"</span></span><br /><br /><span class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">.</span><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\">SetOutput</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">(</span><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\">logsink</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">.</span><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\">GetTraceLogWriter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">(</span><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\">os</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">.</span><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\">Stderr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">))</span></span></code></pre></div></div>\n\n<ul>\n<li>goroutine ID 기반 트랜잭션 컨텍스트 자동 연계</li>\n<li>기존 GetWriterHookStderr()와 호환성 유지</li>\n</ul>"
      },
      {
        "ver": "v0.5.0",
        "hash": "v050-4",
        "product": "Go Agent",
        "type": "New",
        "desc": "<p><code class=\"New\" type=\"1\">New</code> 자동 계측 도구 whatap-go-inst</p>",
        "details": "<p>Go AST 기반 소스코드 자동 계측 CLI 도구를 지원합니다. 소스코드를 직접 수정하지 않고 빌드 시점에 모니터링 코드를 자동 삽입합니다.</p>\n\n<div class=\"language-bash codeBlockContainer theme-code-block\" style=\"--prism-background-color:#292d3e;--prism-color:#f8f8f2\"><div class=\"codeBlockContent\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" class=\"prism-code language-bash codeBlock thin-scrollbar\" style=\"color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#292d3e\"><code class=\"codeBlockLines\"><span class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token comment\" style=\"color:rgb(105,112,152);font-style:italic\"># 설치</span></span><br /><span class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\">go install github.com/whatap/go-api-inst/cmd/whatap-go-inst@latest</span></span><br /><br /><span class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token comment\" style=\"color:rgb(105,112,152);font-style:italic\"># 사용</span></span><br /><span class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\">whatap-go-inst init</span></span><br /><span class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\">whatap-go-inst go build ./...</span></span></code></pre></div></div>\n\n<p><strong>지원 라이브러리</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>웹: Gin, Echo, Fiber, Chi, Gorilla Mux, net/http, FastHTTP</li>\n<li>DB: database/sql, sqlx, GORM</li>\n<li>Redis: Redigo, go-redis (v8, v9)</li>\n<li>NoSQL: MongoDB, Aerospike</li>\n<li>메시지큐: Sarama (IBM/Shopify)</li>\n<li>RPC: gRPC, Kubernetes client-go</li>\n<li>로그: log, logrus, zap</li>\n</ul>"
      },
      {
        "ver": "v0.5.0",
        "hash": "v050-5",
        "product": "Go Agent",
        "type": "New",
        "desc": "<p><code class=\"New\" type=\"1\">New</code> 지원 라이브러리 추가</p>",
        "details": "<table><thead><tr><th>라이브러리</th><th>패키지</th><th>whatap 모듈</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>go-redis v9</td><td>github.com/redis/go-redis/v9</td><td>whatapgoredis</td></tr><tr><td>go-redis v8</td><td>github.com/go-redis/redis/v8</td><td>whatapgoredis</td></tr><tr><td>sqlx</td><td>github.com/jmoiron/sqlx</td><td>whatapsqlx</td></tr><tr><td>MongoDB</td><td>go.mongodb.org/mongo-driver</td><td>whatapmongo</td></tr><tr><td>Aerospike</td><td>github.com/aerospike/aerospike-client-go</td><td>sql.Wrap</td></tr><tr><td>fmt.Print</td><td>fmt</td><td>whatapfmt</td></tr></tbody></table>"
      },
      {
        "ver": "v0.5.0",
        "hash": "v050-6",
        "product": "Go Agent",
        "type": "Feature",
        "desc": "<p><code class=\"Feature\" type=\"1\">Feature</code> 범용 Wrap[T] 함수 (Go 1.18 Generics)</p>",
        "details": "<p>Go 1.18의 Generics를 활용한 범용 Wrap 함수를 추가했습니다.</p>\n\n<div class=\"language-go codeBlockContainer theme-code-block\" style=\"--prism-background-color:#292d3e;--prism-color:#f8f8f2\"><div class=\"codeBlockContent\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" class=\"prism-code language-go codeBlock thin-scrollbar\" style=\"color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#292d3e\"><code class=\"codeBlockLines\"><span class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\">result </span><span class=\"token operator\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">:=</span><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"> trace</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">.</span><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\">Wrap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">(</span><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\">ctx</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"> </span><span class=\"token string\" style=\"color:rgb(195,232,141)\">\"operation\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">func</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">()</span><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"> </span><span class=\"token builtin\" style=\"color:rgb(255,203,107)\">int</span><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">{</span></span><br /><span class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\">    </span><span class=\"token keyword\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">return</span><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"> doSomething</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">()</span></span><br /><span class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:rgb(199,146,234)\">)</span></span></code></pre></div></div>\n\n<ul>\n<li>trace.Wrap[T], trace.WrapError[T], trace.WrapVoid</li>\n<li>sql.Wrap[T], httpc.Wrap[T], method.Wrap[T]</li>\n</ul>"
      },
      {
        "ver": "v0.5.0",
