        "product": "Go Agent",
        "type": "Fixed",
        "desc": "<p><code class=\"Fixed\" type=\"0\">Fixed</code> 에이전트 이름 패턴의 환경변수 처리 버그 수정</p>",
        "details": "<ul>\n<li><code>object_name</code> 설정에서 <code>{env.환경변수이름}</code> 패턴이 정상 동작하지 않던 문제를 수정했습니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"language-ini codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block\" style=\"--prism-color:#bfc7d5;--prism-background-color:#292d3e\"><div class=\"codeBlockContent_biex\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" class=\"prism-code language-ini codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5;background-color:#292d3e\"><code class=\"codeBlockLines_e6Vv\"><span class=\"token-line\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"><span class=\"token comment\" style=\"color:#676e95;font-style:italic\"># 설정 예시</span><br></span><span class=\"token-line\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"><span class=\"token key attr-name\" style=\"color:#c792ea\">object_name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#89ddff\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\" style=\"color:#c3e88d\">{env.SERVER_NAME}-{pid}</span><br></span><span class=\"token-line\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"><br></span><span class=\"token-line\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"><span class=\"token comment\" style=\"color:#676e95;font-style:italic\"># 환경변수: SERVER_NAME=web-server-01</span><br></span><span class=\"token-line\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"><span class=\"token comment\" style=\"color:#676e95;font-style:italic\"># 결과: 에이전트 이름 web-server-01-12345</span><br></span></code></pre><div class=\"buttonGroup__atx\"><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"클립보드에 코드 복사\" title=\"복사\" class=\"clean-btn\"><span class=\"copyButtonIcons_eSgA\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"copyButtonIcon_y97N\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z\"></path></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z\"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>"
      },
      {
