        "hash": "v046",
        "product": "Go Agent",
        "type": "Feature",
        "desc": "<p><code class=\"Feature\" type=\"1\">Feature</code> 프로세스 ID 패턴 지원</p>",
        "details": "<p>에이전트 이름에 프로세스 ID를 포함할 수 있습니다. 같은 서버에서 여러 프로세스 실행 시 유용합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"language-ini codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block\" style=\"--prism-color:#bfc7d5;--prism-background-color:#292d3e\"><div class=\"codeBlockContent_biex\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" class=\"prism-code language-ini codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5;background-color:#292d3e\"><code class=\"codeBlockLines_e6Vv\"><span class=\"token-line\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"><span class=\"token key attr-name\" style=\"color:#c792ea\">object_name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#89ddff\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\" style=\"color:#c3e88d\">myapp-{pid}</span><br></span><span class=\"token-line\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"><span class=\"token comment\" style=\"color:#676e95;font-style:italic\"># 결과: myapp-12345</span><br></span></code></pre><div class=\"buttonGroup__atx\"><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"클립보드에 코드 복사\" title=\"복사\" class=\"clean-btn\"><span class=\"copyButtonIcons_eSgA\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"copyButtonIcon_y97N\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z\"></path></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z\"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>"
