      {
        "ver": "v0.4.6",
        "hash": "v046",
        "product": "Go Agent",
        "type": "Feature",
        "desc": "<p><code class=\"Feature\" type=\"1\">Feature</code> HTTP 상태 코드별 통계</p>",
        "details": "<p>HTTP 상태 코드별로 트랜잭션 통계를 수집합니다.</p>\n<p><strong>5초 통계</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>HTTP 상태코드별 count/time 집계</li>\n<li>200/400/500대 상태별 버킷 집계</li>\n<li>개별 상태코드별 상세 집계</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>5분 통계</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>URL + Status 조합으로 count/time/error 집계</li>\n<li>5분마다 서버로 전송</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>설정 옵션</strong></p>\n<div class=\"language-ini codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block\" style=\"--prism-color:#bfc7d5;--prism-background-color:#292d3e\"><div class=\"codeBlockContent_biex\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" class=\"prism-code language-ini codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5;background-color:#292d3e\"><code class=\"codeBlockLines_e6Vv\"><span class=\"token-line\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"><span class=\"token key attr-name\" style=\"color:#c792ea\">tx_status_meter_enabled</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#89ddff\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\" style=\"color:#c3e88d\">true</span><span class=\"token comment\" style=\"color:#676e95;font-style:italic\">      # 5초 통계 (기본: true)</span><br></span><span class=\"token-line\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"><span class=\"token key attr-name\" style=\"color:#c792ea\">stat_txstatus_enabled</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#89ddff\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\" style=\"color:#c3e88d\">true</span><span class=\"token comment\" style=\"color:#676e95;font-style:italic\">        # 5분 통계 (기본: true)</span><br></span><span class=\"token-line\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"><span class=\"token key attr-name\" style=\"color:#c792ea\">stat_txstatus_max_count</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#89ddff\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\" style=\"color:#c3e88d\">10000</span><span class=\"token comment\" style=\"color:#676e95;font-style:italic\">     # 최대 항목 수</span><br></span></code></pre><div class=\"buttonGroup__atx\"><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"클립보드에 코드 복사\" title=\"복사\" class=\"clean-btn\"><span class=\"copyButtonIcons_eSgA\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"copyButtonIcon_y97N\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z\"></path></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z\"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>"
      },
      {
        "ver": "v0.4.6",
        "hash": "v046",
        "product": "Go Agent",
        "type": "Feature",
        "desc": "<p><code class=\"Feature\" type=\"1\">Feature</code> 쿠버네티스 컨테이너 ID 연계</p>",
        "details": "<p>쿠버네티스 환경에서 컨테이너 ID를 정확히 연계할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><strong>동작 방식</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Go Agent가 실행되면 컨테이너 ID를 <code>container.conf</code> 파일로 생성합니다</li>\n<li>생성된 컨테이너 ID를 사용하여 쿠버네티스 모니터링과 연계합니다</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"language-yaml codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block\" style=\"--prism-color:#bfc7d5;--prism-background-color:#292d3e\"><div class=\"codeBlockContent_biex\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" class=\"prism-code language-yaml codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5;background-color:#292d3e\"><code class=\"codeBlockLines_e6Vv\"><span class=\"token-line\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"><span class=\"token comment\" style=\"color:#676e95;font-style:italic\"># Deployment YAML에 환경변수 추가</span><br></span><span class=\"token-line\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"><span class=\"token key atrule\" style=\"color:#c792ea\">env</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#89ddff\">:</span><br></span><span class=\"token-line\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"><span class=\"token comment\" style=\"color:#676e95;font-style:italic\">  # Go Agent 실행 파일 경로</span><br></span><span class=\"token-line\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#89ddff\">  -</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\" style=\"color:#c792ea\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#89ddff\">:</span> WHATAP_GO_AGENT_PATH<br></span><span class=\"token-line\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\">    <span class=\"token key atrule\" style=\"color:#c792ea\">value</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#89ddff\">:</span> /usr/whatap/agent/whatap_agent_static<br></span><span class=\"token-line\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"><br></span><span class=\"token-line\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"><span class=\"token comment\" style=\"color:#676e95;font-style:italic\">  # 컨테이너 ID가 저장될 경로</span><br></span><span class=\"token-line\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\"><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#89ddff\">  -</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\" style=\"color:#c792ea\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#89ddff\">:</span> WHATAP_CONTAINER_CONF_PATH<br></span><span class=\"token-line\" style=\"color:#bfc7d5\">    <span class=\"token key atrule\" style=\"color:#c792ea\">value</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"color:#89ddff\">:</span> /usr/whatap/agent<br></span></code></pre><div class=\"buttonGroup__atx\"><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"클립보드에 코드 복사\" title=\"복사\" class=\"clean-btn\"><span class=\"copyButtonIcons_eSgA\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"copyButtonIcon_y97N\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M19,21H8V7H19M19,5H8A2,2 0 0,0 6,7V21A2,2 0 0,0 8,23H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,21V7A2,2 0 0,0 19,5M16,1H4A2,2 0 0,0 2,3V17H4V3H16V1Z\"></path></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" class=\"copyButtonSuccessIcon_LjdS\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M21,7L9,19L3.5,13.5L4.91,12.09L9,16.17L19.59,5.59L21,7Z\"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div>"
      }
    ]
  },
